(53, 'PIGEUX', 'uploads/53/game.png', 'You are a Pigeon who must go around the city trying to persuade business men not to jump off buildings by retrieving items from their home.', 'The player controls a pigeon in 3rd person view, in a 3D environment depicting above the clouds skyscrapers. Fly near businessmen standing on top of the buildings to hear their lamentations. The player must find the correspondent window where he must choose one item to bring back. Time is ticking as the men slowly walk towards the roof ledges...\r\n\r\nNOTE: The bug is now fixed. Enjoy :)\r\n\r\nYou can reach us at scapedoor@gmail.com', 'uploads/53/game.zip', 'http://dl.dropbox.com/u/28555190/WebPlayer/WebPlayer.html', 'Lisbon, Portugal', 'uploads/53/team.png', 'João Miguel Rodrigues;\r\nAndré Sanchez Silva;\r\nFrederico Lira Pereira;\r\nLeandro Reis;\r\nMário Campos;\r\nAntónio Silva;', 'CC BY-NC', 'Unity3D', 533, 169, '2012-04-01 11:48:30', '2012-04-03 04:08:06', '05e454ea6fb04dde800e839ddd29686b'),
