(55, 'Washing Machine Carnage: The Cleansing', 'uploads/55/game.jpg', 'What if your body was a washing machine and you had to wash your enemies before you can kill them?', 'This washing machine is on a quest to cleanse humanity of its sins... and save the videogame industry!\r\nYou control the machine. First, swallow impure humans (if their shirt is the right color, that is); then, flee away from the angry mob while you wash your victims, and when they''re all nice and clean, spew out their limbs on your pursuers! \r\n----------------- \r\n/!\\ plug in a X360 controller or equivalent before launching the game /!\\', 'http://files.studio-a.cc/wmc/washingmachinecarnage.html', '', 'Internet', '', 'Pierre Delage (@PierreDelage) -- \r\nSandro Bordier (@Drokarn) -- \r\nRomane Govin -- \r\nChloé Ravallec -- \r\nAurélien Carlier -- \r\nSimon Dutertre (@SimonDutertre) -- \r\nMartin Dinet (@MartinDinet) -- \r\nRobin Vilain (@Acccent) -- \r\nGeoffroy Calis', 'CC BY-NC', 'Unity3D', 359, 41, '2012-04-01 12:32:22', '2012-04-02 06:53:34', 'a0ebdd7e5064ccdd514bd347524633da'),
