(293, 'The Guy That Should Not Be Here', 'uploads/293/game.png', 'Game where your arms are controlled by a psychopath who keeps firing guns at innocent people. You must turn away from them and run', 'Why do we fight? Why do we kill? What makes us enter a game world and start shooting innocents for no reason? What if... your choice to kill was made for you?  Would you embrace the darkness or would you fight against a game that tells you what you are supposed to be.\r\n\r\nThere are two endings to this game. Which one would you choose?\r\n\r\nGame Located at Either Link\r\nhttp://mggsound.com/files/GameJam/TheGuyThatShouldNotBeHereFullGame.zip\r\n\r\nhttps://files.me.com/montygoulet/evz13e', 'http://mggsound.com/files/GameJam/TheGuyThatShouldNotBeHereFullGame.zip', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0BfHeAwm1a4', 'Austin, USA', '', 'Monty Goulet\r\nEntropic Flip', 'CC BY-NC', 'Unreal', 14, 3, '2012-04-03 20:14:31', '2012-04-04 02:30:57', '9f399f6f617096bd2a45ddb1288a538e'),
(58, 'HeartBeat', 'uploads/58/game.jpg', 'Imagine a constant rumble in a pad throughout the game,your heartbeat. Then at the end, you die and it just stops. Physical emotion.', 'Escape the desert.\r\nPress A to beat heart faster.\r\nAvoid death.\r\n\r\nUnzip and run setup.exe\r\nThis game requires an Xbox or compatible game controller with rumble so you can feel the emotion.', 'uploads/58/game.zip', '', 'Internet', 'uploads/58/team.jpg', 'Code by Hans Wannop\r\nGraphics by Lucy Hoskins', 'CC BY-NC', 'XNA', 285, 50, '2012-04-01 12:53:31', '2012-04-01 14:05:04', '1319658e0f79276e936f6c7309ecef2a'),
(59, 'Babby''a First Kill', '', 'You live in a little house made of guns. You need many guns to fight invaders but also need to keep a roof on top of your many children.', 'My game started as an honest take on the theme, but over time it went further and further from the given theme, so currently the only thing similar to what I started with are the babies and the idea of using building pieces as weapons.\r\n\r\nThis game is a fast-paced BABY MUD FLINGING GAME where two babies clash in order to see who''s the babiest of all.\r\n\r\nThe game requires Joysticks (preferably xbox 360 controllers). Controls are described in-game.', '', '', 'Helsinki, Finland', '', 'Arvi Teikari', 'CC BY', 'Other', 156, 0, '2012-04-01 13:15:28', '2012-04-01 13:15:28', '6125243f5d307d0d15be1f2ab02594af'),
(60, 'Babbys First Kill', '', 'You live in a little house made of guns. You need many guns to fight invaders but you also need to keep a roof on top of your many children.', 'This game doesn''t really represent the theme at all. It started with good intentions but soon twisted and turned into something else.\r\n\r\nYou need an Xbox 360 controller or other gamepad with two sticks and shoulderpads.', '', '', 'Helsinki, Finland', '', 'Arvi Teikari', 'CC BY', 'Other', 108, 0, '2012-04-01 13:19:20', '2012-04-01 13:19:20', 'ec0bc527c260e49efea10cb41ccdb96c'),
(61, 'Shuriken Frenzy', 'uploads/61/game.png', 'A game where if you touch the floor you die. the only way to progress is to kill enemies and use their bodies as platforms.', 'In shuriken frenzy, you embody a ninja in his quest to slide down a river of molten lava. Kill your enemies to use them as magma surfing material, avoid obstacles at all costs and go as far as you can!', 'uploads/61/game.zip', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8a2ZCoO2rCc', 'Internet', '', 'Léo Mullier - Game design, Programming /\r\nCorentin Lemasson - Game design, Programming /\r\nMatthieu Bavagnoli - Game & level design /\r\nSylvain NGuyen - 3D art /\r\nLucas Jeanneau - 3D art /\r\nStéphanie Ruffenac - 2D art /\r\nSybil Collas - Producing, Music /\r\nAlexandre Papiachvili - Sound Design', 'CC BY-NC-SA', 'Unity3D', 158, 16, '2012-04-01 13:24:46', '2012-04-02 10:36:20', '7492ea79ed764281ceb7a7bf8d686706'),
